<Layout title="Tax Residency in Singapore: The 183-Day Rule & Non-Resident Rates | SalaryCalculator.sg" description="Complete guide to Singapore tax residency rules. Understand the 183-day rule, non-resident tax rates, the two-year administrative concession, and how to determine your tax status.">
